  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2095108">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2095108/" class="title-link">原不必如此好看</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2095108"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2026462/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2026462-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2026462/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小庄</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-06-26"
      class="main-meta">2009-06-26 03:03:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2095108_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  年轻时候，看奥里亚娜•法拉奇的传记，打定主意成为那样的女人——那也可说是生平第一次立志，想要做个心怀天下的女记者，而且是明星级别的。无奈彼时还在理工科院校混，后来进媒体做文化报道，数年后走回了科技报道的路子，然后依稀明白：从此要老老实实写字看书做采访，只...

